## File Structure

### React Web (Before)

```
src/
├── components/
│   ├── Button.tsx
│   └── ProductCard.tsx
├── pages/
│   ├── HomePage.tsx
│   └── products/
│       └── ProductsPage.tsx
└── main.tsx
```

### Expo (After — using Expo Router)

```
app/                        ← Expo Router pages (file = route)
├── (tabs)/                 ← Tab group
│   ├── index.tsx           ← Home tab
│   └── products.tsx        ← Products tab
├── products/
│   └── [id].tsx            ← Product detail (dynamic route)
├── login.tsx
└── _layout.tsx             ← Root layout
components/
├── Button.tsx
└── ProductCard.tsx
hooks/
└── useProducts.ts
constants/
└── Colors.ts
```

