## Storage

| Web | React Native |
|-----|-------------|
| `localStorage.setItem('key', val)` | `await AsyncStorage.setItem('key', val)` |
| `localStorage.getItem('key')` | `await AsyncStorage.getItem('key')` |
| `localStorage.removeItem('key')` | `await AsyncStorage.removeItem('key')` |
| Sensitive data (tokens) | `expo-secure-store` (encrypted keychain) |

```ts
import * as SecureStore from 'expo-secure-store';

// Store token securely
await SecureStore.setItemAsync('token', tokenValue);
const token = await SecureStore.getItemAsync('token');
await SecureStore.deleteItemAsync('token');
```

