## Common Patterns

### Conditional Rendering — Identical

```tsx
{isLoading ? <ActivityIndicator /> : <ProductList />}
{error && <Text style={{ color: 'red' }}>{error}</Text>}
```

> Use `ActivityIndicator` instead of custom spinners for loading states.

### Safe Area (Notch / Status Bar)

```tsx
import { SafeAreaView } from 'react-native-safe-area-context';

// Wrap screen content to avoid notch/home indicator overlap
<SafeAreaView style={{ flex: 1 }}>
    <YourContent />
</SafeAreaView>
```

