## Migration Checklist

- [ ] Create Expo app: `npx create-expo-app@latest MyApp` (SDK 55 default template uses `/src` folder structure)
- [ ] Enable TypeScript: project is TypeScript by default
- [ ] Verify New Architecture is active (required in SDK 55 — legacy architecture no longer supported)
- [ ] Use development builds instead of Expo Go for testing (Expo Go is being phased out)
- [ ] Replace all `div` → `View`, `p`/`span`/`h1..h6` → `Text`
- [ ] Replace `button` → `Pressable` + `Text`
- [ ] Replace `input[type=text]` → `TextInput` with `onChangeText`
- [ ] Replace `img` → `Image` with `source={{ uri: ... }}`
- [ ] Replace CSS / `className` → `StyleSheet.create()` objects (or NativeWind)
- [ ] Replace `onClick` → `onPress`
- [ ] Replace `React Router` with `Expo Router` (`app/` folder = routes)
- [ ] Replace `<Link to>` → `<Link href>` from `expo-router`
- [ ] Replace `useNavigate()` → `useRouter()` from `expo-router`
- [ ] Replace `useParams()` → `useLocalSearchParams()` from `expo-router`
- [ ] Replace `localStorage` → `AsyncStorage` / `expo-secure-store`
- [ ] Replace `window.*` / `document.*` → Expo SDK equivalents
- [ ] Wrap screen root in `SafeAreaView`
- [ ] Replace spinner `div` → `ActivityIndicator`
- [ ] Wrap list with `FlatList` (not `ScrollView + map`)
- [ ] Add `EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL` to `.env`
- [ ] Test on iOS and Android (real devices or development builds)

